high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the book shelves.
Pick a pencil up from the book shelves.
Turn and walk towards the desk with the computer and stand in front of it.
Put the pencil in the white cup.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn around and stand in front of the shorter shelves on the right.
Put the cup on the middle shelf on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a pencil on a shelf.

high_descs: Move forward then turn left again to face the book shelf.
Take the pencil from the top of the book shelf.
Turn around, then move forward, then turn left to go to the desk.
Place the pencil in the mug on the desk.
Pick up the mug on the desk.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right to approach the shelf to the right of the dresser.
Place the mug on the second shelf, toward the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pencil in it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to face the bookshelf.
Take the pencil off the top of the bookshelf next to the plant.
Walk across the room to the desk.
Set the pencil down in the coffee cup.
Pick up the cup with the pencil in it.
Walk across the room to the cabinet next to the bookshelf with the tissues on it.
Set the cup with the pencil in it down next to the tissues.
anns.task_desc: Put a coffee cup with a pencil in it next to the tissues on the cabinet.
